programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep20
programme.desc: Ezgi ingin berjumpa dengan Serdar sekali lagi untuk menebus kesilapannya. Dia meminta Cansu untuk mengatur pertemuan lain. Kali ini, dia bertekad untuk bertindak dengan betul dan mempengaruhi Serdar. Dia perlukan zgr untuk ini. Jadi dia menerima tawaran zgr. Mereka membuat perjanjian. Ezgi akan bertindak seperti teman wanita zgr untuk satu malam, dan sebagai balasan zgr akan mengajarnya apa yang perlu dilakukan untuk menarik perhatian Serdar. Walau bagaimanapun, perjanjian ini akan mempunyai keputusan yang berbeza untuk kedua-duanya.

programme.title: Poskad Dari Alhambra Ep03

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S12 Ep10
programme.desc: Rancangan ini memaparkan Chef Naem yang akan berkongsi 3 menu masakan yang mudah dan enak. Dalam episod kali ini, Chef akan menyediakan Roti John dapur bujang, Kari Kepala Ikan dapur bujang dan Mi Ladna dapur bujang.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep14
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep30
programme.desc: zgr menjadi marah apabila dia mengetahui bahawa Tolga ialah bos Ezgi. Ezgi segera berhenti. Tetapi Tolga tidak akan selesa sehingga dia mendapat La Gabbia, dia telah pun membuat perancangan untuk meletakkan Ezgi dalam situasi yang sukar dengan sokongan Gizem. Dia mengambil kesempatan daripada kelemahan zgr untuk Ezgi. Apabila bercakap mengenai Ezgi, ia menjadi lebih sukar bagi zgr untuk membuat keputusan menentang kehendak Tolga. Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian.

programme.desc: Kisah Atan dan Fitri adalah pelajar universiti dalam bidang Kesusasteraan Melayu. Untuk semesta ini, Atan dan Fitri ditugaskan untuk membuat satu kajian mengenai Puteri Cahaya Penama. Namun apa yang ditemui hanyalah suatu misteri!

programme.title: Tok Guru Ep13
programme.desc: Jacob dapat telegram dari Mr Johnson yang ajak Jacob aturkan perlawanan bola persahabatan antara pelajar pondok dan pelajar VI. Jacob maklumkan pada Roslan dan perkara itu dibawa ke pengetahuan Tok Guru Nik Ahmad. Tok Guru Nik Ahmah setuju untuk menyahut cabaran itu. Tok Guru Nik Ahmad mula melatih pelajar pondoknya main bola. Tapi Cikgu Roslan kemudian cadangkan agar dibuat pencarian siapa pelajar pondok yang sehat dan kuat untuk menjadi team bola mereka.

programme.title: Sembang Selebriti S6 Ep08
programme.desc: Sembang selebriti merupakan rancangan bual bicara bersama selebriti yang menceritakan tentang pengalaman mereka di dalam dunia seni tanahair yang boleh dijadikan sumber inspirasi.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep21
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. Ozan, yang menyaksikan detik-detik ini, tidak tahu apa yang perlu dilakukan. Adalah sangat penting bagi Ozan untuk bekerjasama dengan Ezgi, walaupun dia bercakap dengan zgr dan cuba membetulkan keadaan ia tidak berjaya. Sementara itu, kejutan kedua menanti Ezgi. Dalam menghadapi kejadian ini, Ezgi menyoal dirinya sendiri dan menganggap dia bertindak salah dengan zgr. Dia mahu membetulkan hubungannya dengan zgr. Keinginan Ezgi untuk datang ke majlis perkahwinan membuatkan zgr gembira. Kedua-duanya bersedia untuk bermain permainan, tidak menyedari apa yang akan berlaku kepada mereka.

programme.title: Nargil Ep05
programme.desc: Bolehkah Hamed menyelamatkan nyawa Ratu Mehrafrooz atau dia hanya menimbulkan lebih banyak masalah?

programme.title: My Sweet Madu
programme.desc: Sebuah kisah komedi perkahwinan Farel bersama isterinya Intan dan Bella.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019) Ep05
programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Perang Bibir S1 Ep09
programme.desc: Nabila Huda dan Issey kembali bersaing. Nabila Huda, yang mengetuai kumpulan perempuan, digandingkan bersama Sherry Al-Hadad dan Ramona Zam Zam menentang kumpulan lelaki yang dipimpin oleh Issey yang digandingkan bersama Dennis Yin dan Izzue Islam. Kedua dua kumpulan perlu menari sepadan dengan rentak lagu yang dimainkan. Markah akan diambil kira daripada kekuatan jeritan para penonton. Pertandingan untuk memenangi RM6,000 sememangnya susah kerana peserta juga perlu bersaing di dalam 2 mini games. Markah tertinggi di penghujung rancangan akan menjadi juara untuk episod ini. Kumpulan lelaki yang mengumpul lebih markah telah diistihar sebagai pemenang.

programme.title: Trend Setter S3 Ep13
programme.desc: Episod Trend Setter kali ini Nabil akan berjumpa dengan pelumba basikal Negara, Sofian Nabil Omar. Nabil juga akan berjumpa dengan pengumpul jersey vintage Malaysia yang mempunyai jersey-jersey Malaysia yang sukar ditemui dan didapati.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep15
programme.desc: Memaparkan Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep31
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.title: Lie After Lie Ep01
programme.desc: Semasa di penjara kerana jenayah yang tidak dilakukannya, Eun Su melahirkan seorang anak perempuan yang dihantar untuk dibesarkan oleh ibu mertuanya

programme.title: Resepi Moyang S4 Ep13
programme.desc: Resepi Moyang merupakan sebuah rancangan memasak yang mengetengahkan masakan tradisional dari serata Malaysia. Dalam episod ini, hos akan belajar memasak masakan kaum Baba Nyonya iaitu Ayam Pongteh, Kari Ayam Kapitan dan Kuih Onde Onde. Dihoskan oleh Alaika Sahrin

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S6 Ep13
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Naem tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat. Untuk episod ini, Naem akan memasak Ayam Goreng Halia dan Zalabia sejenis cucur yang manis yang berasal dari timur tenggah.

programme.title: Instafamous
programme.desc: 3 pelajar sekolah menengah melakukan segala yang mereka mampu untuk menjadi terkenal di media sosial.

programme.title: Tok Guru Ep12
programme.desc: Mr Johnson balik ke KL bincang dengan Headmaster Mr Daniel untuk buat pertandingan persahabatan dengan pelajar pondok Tok Guru Nik Ahmad. Mereka kata simboliknya nak tunjukkan bangsa dan empayar British mereka masih gagah dan berkuasa. Daniel setuju kerana ia boleh jadi bahan latihan sebelum bertanding dan berlawan dengan team Penang Free School,English College dan MCKK.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.title: OH! S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Oh! adalah sebuah program akustik baru. Oh! menampilkan vokalis serta artis-artis yang kini sedang popular atau baru dengan lagu single solo/kumpulan.

programme.desc: Cikgu Maria gembira setelah mendapat tahu bahawa dia akan menjadi seorang cikgu di sebuah sekolah menengah, tetapi selepas memasuki sekolah tersebut, segalanya berlainan dengan harapannya. programme.title: Kuba Guling Karipap Pusing
programme.desc: Pertelingkahan antara dua orang wanita akibat salah faham . Seorang wanita yang berniaga kuih di sebuah gerai membantu seorang wanita lain dengan mengambilnya sebagi pembantu dan akhirnya membantunya memulakan perniagaan bersamanya. Salah faham mula berlaku apabila kuih yang diperkenalkan mula mendapat perhatian ramai dan wanita yang dibantunya berkawan dengan lelaki yang selama ini menjadi pujaannya.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep19
programme.desc: Mengisahkan semasa Eliza bersama bodyguardnya Danial dia nyaris dilanggar. Mereka syak Amran seorang kakitangan Eliza melakukan cubaan tersebut. Hubungan percintaan Eliza dengan Rashid masih berterusan. Farish sebagai bodyguard, masih meneruskan jagaan keselamatan kepada Adam. Dia beberapa kali menyelamatkan Adam dari dipukul oleh Zack dan rakan kumpulannnya. Adam dikatakan membocor rahsia kumpulan kepada polis sehingga ada di kalangan mereka yang telah tertangkap. Ryan bodyguard Datin Maziah, dia menunjukkan photo perhubungan Datin Maziah dengan Badrul kepada Dato Zailani. Akhirnya Dato Zailani menceraikan Datin Maziah. Di akhir episod, Amran melihat Rashid berbaik-baik dengan Eliza, dia memberi amaran kepada Rashid untuk membocorkan rahsia mereka kepada Eliza sekiranya tidak memberi wang kepadanya.

programme.desc: Hanim yang masuk ke rumah pengasih berkawan dengan Aira dan sering di buli oleh dua lagi penghuni di rumah pengasih maria dan Nita.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep18
programme.desc: Mengisahkan semasa Eliza bersama bodyguardnya Danial dia nyaris dilanggar. Mereka syak Amran seorang kakitangan Eliza melakukan cubaan tersebut. programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep10
programme.desc: Akil yang sedang tidur telah dijejutkan oleh saka Kimchi yang menuntut dia menolongnya pulang ke Korea. Menurut Kimchi Akil telah menolong tiga daripada kawannya iaitu Jendul, Big Foot dan Mayang Kasturi dan kali ini giliran dia pula ditolong. Akil ingin tahu bagaimana Kimchi boleh sampai kemari. Mengikut Kimchi dia datang bersama tuannya tetapi tuannya meninggal kerana tercekek tulang semasa makan di sebuah restoran. Kerana tiada bertuan, dia terus tinggal di retoran itu dan mengacau pengunjung restoran. Tuan punya restoran telah mengupah Bomoh Tok Misai untuk menghalaunya. Tok Misai telah menangkapnya dan sejak itu dia diperhambakan oleh Tok Misai hinggalah To Misai meninggal. Akil masukkan Kimchi kedalam suatu kotak dan menghantarnya ke Korea melaui pos laju. Sehingga masa ini, ke empat-empat saka itu iaitu Jendol, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi telah dibebaskan daripada kekuasaan Tok Misai. Kimchi yang sepatunya berlepas ke Korea telah keluar daripada bungkusan dan datang semula berkumpul dengan tiga teman sakanya. Akil tidak tahu yang Kimchi tidak berangkat ke Korea. Akil berharap dia tidak lagi diganggu oleh empat saka itu.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep17
programme.desc: Dzulkarnain telah dianiayai dengan ilmu hitam oleh Manuja menyebabkan dia sakit, namun diselamatkan oleh para pendekar sakti. Dalam pertempuran itu, Jagat mati tetapi Nading dan Lang Kajai dapat melarikan diri. Dzulkarnain yang sebenarnya sudah nazak, akhirnya mati.

programme.title: Iblis
programme.desc: Sejak mereka menduduki rumah tersebut, banyak perkara pelik yang pasangan ini lalui terutamanya Kim. Kim sentiasa diganggu dengan kehadiran figura yang mengganggunya. Den juga rasa sama.

programme.title: Model Family Ep03
programme.desc: Sebuah keluarga ibu bapa tunggal (Yu Xiang dan Tong Tong) berpindah ke kawasan kejiranan baharu di mana kehidupan semua orang nampak sempurna. Walau bagaimanapun, keadaan mungkin kelihatan cerah di luar, rahsia gelap dan seram menyerbu setiap keluarga dari dalam, dan tidak ada yang benar-benar seperti yang kelihatan.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan mayat Zai ditemui oleh orang kampung Paya Besar dengan kesan jerutan di leher pada esok paginya. Mayat Zai diuruskan oleh keluarganya. Salah seorang yang hadir adalah sepupu Zai, Sulaiman. Sulaiman terkejut bila melihat kesan kematian Zai seperti pernah dilihatnya 50 tahun dulu iaitu kematian Awang. Long Husin kini menjadi boneka Awang untuk mencari 13 perawan

programme.title: Bopeng
programme.desc: Helmi Yusof - Bo (Nabil Ahmad) dan Peng (Johan As'ari) merupakan dua orang sahabat baik yang tinggal bersama dan bekerja di sebuah restoran makanan segera yang sama iaitu Opiel Secret Pizza. Peng yang terkenal dengan sikap peramah dan mesra setiap kali menjawab panggilan yang dari pelanggan untuk membuat pesanan pizza; manakala Bo terkenal dengan kepantasan dan kecekapannya menghantar pesanan pizza kepada pelanggan.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.2 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lekaki yang membela hantu raya yang di warisi oleh ayahnya dengan terpaksa. Namun lama kelamaan dia mula suka dengan saka belaan tersebut. Setelah bertahun-tahun dan usianya yang menghampiri kematian, pak Harun mula sedar dan cuba membuang hantu raya tersebut yang mula menganggu penduduk kampung. Apatah lagi anak gadisnya putus tunang akibat dia membela hantu raya tersebut. Pak Harun akhirnya berjaya membuang hantu raya tersebut dengan bantuan seorang ustaz. Pak harun akhirnya meninggal dunia, anak dan isterinya berpindah selepas kematian pak harun

programme.desc: Pada zaman kanak-kanaknya, Riana tinggal di sebuah pekan kecil bersama ayah dan ibunya yang menjalankan perniagaan rumah pengebumian. Musibah yang datang memerlukan mereka berpindah ke rumah Pakcik Johan di Jakarta dan Riana bertemu dengan anak patung Riani. Riana semakin dewasa dan suatu hari telah dilawati oleh Puan Klara, seorang guru kaunselor di sekolahnya yang ingin mengetahui sebab Riana tidak hadir ke sekolah dan mencadangkan Riana untuk dipulihkan. Musibah menimpa ibu bapa Riana. Puan Klara datang lagi bersama Hendro, Lusi dan Anggi, untuk membantu Riana beramah mesra. Tetapi, kehadiran mereka mencetuskan masalah yang lebih besar.

programme.desc: Pada zaman kanak-kanaknya, Riana tinggal di sebuah pekan kecil bersama ayah dan ibunya yang menjalankan perniagaan rumah pengebumian. Musibah yang datang memerlukan mereka berpindah ke rumah Pakcik Johan di Jakarta dan Riana bertemu dengan anak patung Riani. Riana semakin dewasa dan suatu hari telah dilawati oleh Puan Klara, seorang guru kaunselor di sekolahnya yang ingin mengetahui sebab Riana tidak hadir ke sekolah dan mencadangkan Riana untuk dipulihkan. Musibah menimpa ibu bapa Riana. Puan Klara datang lagi bersama Hendro, Lusi dan Anggi, untuk membantu Riana beramah mesra. Tetapi, kehadiran mereka mencetuskan masalah yang lebih besar.

programme.title: Rambo Last Blood
programme.desc: Kehidupan damai John Rambo terganggu apabila Gabriela, cucu kawannya, hilang di Mexico. Dia memutuskan untuk membebaskannya daripada cengkaman kartel tempatan, memulakan kitaran membalas dendam.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep10
programme.desc: Akil yang sedang tidur telah dijejutkan oleh saka Kimchi yang menuntut dia menolongnya pulang ke Korea. Menurut Kimchi Akil telah menolong tiga daripada kawannya iaitu Jendul, Big Foot dan Mayang Kasturi dan kali ini giliran dia pula ditolong. Akil ingin tahu bagaimana Kimchi boleh sampai kemari. Mengikut Kimchi dia datang bersama tuannya tetapi tuannya meninggal kerana tercekek tulang semasa makan di sebuah restoran. Kerana tiada bertuan, dia terus tinggal di retoran itu dan mengacau pengunjung restoran. Tuan punya restoran telah mengupah Bomoh Tok Misai untuk menghalaunya. Tok Misai telah menangkapnya dan sejak itu dia diperhambakan oleh Tok Misai hinggalah To Misai meninggal. Akil masukkan Kimchi kedalam suatu kotak dan menghantarnya ke Korea melaui pos laju. Sehingga masa ini, ke empat-empat saka itu iaitu Jendol, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi telah dibebaskan daripada kekuasaan Tok Misai. Kimchi yang sepatunya berlepas ke Korea telah keluar daripada bungkusan dan datang semula berkumpul dengan tiga teman sakanya. Akil tidak tahu yang Kimchi tidak berangkat ke Korea. Akil berharap dia tidak lagi diganggu oleh empat saka itu.

programme.title: The Presence
programme.desc: Aom dihantui mimpi ngeri yang tidak dapat dijelaskan. Semasa melawat neneknya, dia mendapat tahu bahawa neneknya yang kelihatan lebih mati daripada hidup sedang melayan dan memberi makan kepada hantu. Adakah Aom akan menerima nasibnya?

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep9
programme.desc: Mengisahkan semasa Eliza bersama bodyguardnya Danial dia nyaris dilanggar. Mereka syak Amran seorang kakitangan Eliza melakukan cubaan tersebut. Hubungan percintaan Eliza dengan Rashid masih berterusan. Farish sebagai bodyguard, masih meneruskan jagaan keselamatan kepada Adam. Dia beberapa kali menyelamatkan Adam dari dipukul oleh Zack dan rakan kumpulannnya. Adam dikatakan membocor rahsia kumpulan kepada polis sehingga ada di kalangan mereka yang telah tertangkap. Ryan bodyguard Datin Maziah, dia menunjukkan photo perhubungan Datin Maziah dengan Badrul kepada Dato Zailani. Akhirnya Dato Zailani menceraikan Datin Maziah. Di akhir episod, Amran melihat Rashid berbaik-baik dengan Eliza, dia memberi amaran kepada Rashid untuk membocorkan rahsia mereka kepada Eliza sekiranya tidak memberi wang kepadanya.

programme.title: Sindiket
programme.desc: Diilhamkan daripada kisah benar, ia memaparkan sindiket pemerdagangan manusia dan menceritakan kisah seorang wanita yang ditipu oleh teman lelakinya. Dia telah dijual ke rumah pelacuran di mana dia dibius dan dipaksa untuk menjual dirinya.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Empat beradik membawa haluan masing-masing selepas bapa mereka dimasukkan ke sebuah hospital sakit jiwa. Malik memilih untuk menjadi peninju manakala Sidi memilih jalan gelap dan diperalatkan sindiket pencurian berlian. Malik memenangi pertandingan tinju anjuran Joe Martino. Adiknya, Sidi dipaksa untuk bertarung dengan Malik jika tidak mahu kehilangan keluarganya.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Kisah seorang graduan universiti bekerja sebagai budak pejabat yang pada suatu hari didatangi oleh seekor monyet cerdik tersesat ke rumahnya. Suatu hari berlaku krisis di pejabatnya. Budak pejabat itu perlu segera mencari jalan untuk menyelesaikan masalah dan dalam proses itu hampir membahayakan nyawanya sendiri. Dengan bantuan monyet tersebut, dia berjaya mengatasi banyak masalah dan berjaya menyelamatkan pekerjaannya.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Boss
programme.desc: Tiga gadis bersama seorang kapten membanteras kumpulan jahat yang melanggar undang-undang. Mereka berhadapan dengan Malik yang menjalankan kegiatan pemerdagangan manusia. Pelbagai rintangan perlu mereka tempuhi apabila salah seorang anggota mereka, Clara diculik kumpulan tersebut ketika cuba menyelamatkan tahanan lain. Mereka pun memulakan misi untuk mencari Clara dan menjatuhkan kumpulan Malik.

programme.title: Keluarga 99
programme.desc: Azam, peguam penceraian yang tidak mahu berkahwin kerana fobia selepas mengendalikan banyak kes permasalahan rumahtangga. Dijodohkan oleh kakak angkatnya bersama seorang gadis kampung bernama Marlia. Azam akhirnya bersetuju dengan rancangan itu namun timbul masalah apabila Maria cuba digoda oleh sepupunya sendiri.

programme.title: Sahabat
programme.desc: Kisah tiga sahabat yang bertemu ketika di penjara ingin memulakan hidup mereka kembali bersama- sama setelah keluar dari penjara. Pelbagai dugaan dan cabaran yang perlu ditempuhi mereka sebelum akhirnya berjaya mencapai apa yang mereka hajati.

programme.title: Mr.Os
programme.desc: Os, seorang pemuda biasa yang tidak mempunyai banyak harta mendapat durian runtuh apabila datuknya mewarisi wang berjumlah RM500,000 kepadanya. Dia perlu menghabiskan wang tersebut dalam masa 21 hari - sekiranya gagal, harta warisan tersebut akan diberi kepada sebuah syarikat. Syaratnya Os tidak boleh membeli aset atau tanah untuk simpanan sendiri. Meski sudah berbelanja boros baki wang masih tersisa.

programme.desc: Dipandang rendah oleh keluarga dan masyarakat kerana gagal dalam peperiksaan, Os mula mencipta satu formula. programme.desc: Malik menembak dua orang pembelot setelah diarah oleh Chief. Malik dan Amir, anak Datuk Ali di mana keduanya rakan lama bertemu semula di sebuah kelab malam. Persengketaan berlaku antara Chief dan Malik apabila dia dilihat sebagai pembelot yang telah mencuri wang kumpulan Chief.

programme.desc: Seorang lelaki berjanji dengan teman wanitanya bahawa dia akan bersamanya pada hari lahirnya iaitu dua hari kemudian. Kemudian pada petang itu semasa berhenti untuk minum di sebuah bar, dia tersilap diculik kerana menyerupai anak seorang jutawan.

programme.title: Khalifahkah Aku
programme.desc: Kisah Fatah anak kepada Datuk Amran dan Datin Marissa. Kedua-dua ibu bapanya sibuk dengan urusan dunia dan kerap alpa dalam urusan ibadat seharian. Mereka menghantar Fatah belajar di sekolah agama dengan harapan dia menjadi anak yang soleh.

programme.title: Tmo Misteri Bulan Madu

programme.title: Ijam
programme.desc: seorang pemuda yang berminat dengan seorang gadis kampung. Sanggup bekerja keras untuk memenuhi impianya. Namun, pelbagai syarat dan rintangan yang terpaksa dia lalui dalam perjalanannya itu.

programme.title: Mv Seleksi Sinema Ep7
programme.desc: Seleksi lagu-lagu menarik untuk hiburan anda

programme.title: Musafir Ke?
programme.desc: Kisah seorang suami yang tidak pernah berenggang dengan isteri terpaksa berpisah dengan isterinya apabila perlu menjaga anaknya yang dalam pantang, dan paling mengharukan ialah si isteri terkandas di rumah anak akibat lockdown. Keadaan semakin kacau bilau apabila beliau didatangi oleh seseorang yang tidak di kenali dalam bulan Ramadan.

programme.title: My Stupid Boss
programme.desc: Seorang perempuan indonesia datang ke kuala lumpur mengikut suaminya. Setelah berada di kuala lumpur dia berhasrat untuk bekerja di syarikat milik rakan suaminya. Majikannya itu merupakan seorang yang memiliki sikap dan perangai yang membuatnya sentiasa berada dalam keadaan serba salah dan tertekan. Sikap majikannya yang tidak mahu membayar hutang, menuduhnya mengambil wang syarikat dan tidak membayar gaji menyebabkan dia nekad untuk berhenti kerja. Namun kisah berakhir apabila dia bersetuju untuk bekerja semula apabila majikannya memintanya menguruskan kerja-kerja kebajikan membaiki rumah anak yatim.

programme.title: Dosen Killer Bikin Hati Gemeter
programme.desc: Melati tidak mempedulikan pelajarannya sehingga membuatkan Oma Wita tekesal dan mahu membatalkan segala kemudahannya. Melati, mahu tidak mahu, terpaksa menamatkan pengajian di kolej di bawah bimbingan Arjuna yang terkenal sebagai pensyarah tegas.

programme.title: Cinta 2 Pilihan Ep219

programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep181
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.desc: Stylish Man The Chef is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are Big Stars Come to Cook and Five-Star Cooking Show. Stylish Man The Chef containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: New Taiwan Go (M) Ep2773
programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside

programme.title: Stories In Taiwan (T) Ep1059
programme.desc: In a playful and relaxed style, the host went deep into the corners of various towns and villages in Taiwan, looking for the uniqueness, introduced the special local customs and traditions.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep122
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health(M) Ep235236
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep473
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Lost Romance(M) Ep2627
programme.desc: Xiao-En Zheng is an ordinary editor for romance novels who always dreams that one day a rich hunk would come and save her. One of her enjoyable times is to peek out the window to see Tian-Xing He, who is a CEO working in the next building. Her world changes completely when an accident occurs. She time travels into her novel. Not knowing where she is, she sees Tian-Xing He walking towards her.

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Book of Love
programme.desc: A casino PR in Macau receives a classic novel 84, Charing Cross Road. She sends back the novel with a letter to where it came from as she does not like it. A real estate agent in California receives the novel and as it does not belong to him, he sends it back with a letter as well. The two form a relationship after all the back and forth.

programme.title: Dragon Master: Dragon Spell
programme.desc: The Dragon King is locked in a seal by the Dragon Master for 500 years, and his daughter must travel back in time to 500 years ago to kill the Dragon Master, in order to reverse the act. Little did she know that the Dragon King and Dragon Master were close friends back then

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quins trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Missbehavior
programme.desc: A group of friends who are formerly close but now somewhat estranged, unite to help one of their own who is in trouble at work. In this hilarious comedy, the friends must find a replacement bottle of breast milk before the end of the day as chaos breaks out!

programme.title: Dearest Anita
programme.desc: Based on real events, the movie follows the footsteps of the fans of Hong Kong Canto-pop diva Anita Mui. After the death of the popstar, fans from different walks of life risk arrest to track down handwritten cards, letters and other possessions from Anita Mui to preserve their idols memory.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Hotel Deluxe
programme.desc: Bai Xing Hotel is a five-star luxury hotel located in Qian Dao Lake, Hang Zhou, with a service level only worthy of a four-star hotel. The head office sent Cruella Koo, a tough executive, to lead reforms for the hotel and upgrade the employees performance to reach the five-star level.

programme.title: Romantic Dream
programme.desc: Dino meets his dream girl Mandy and falls in love with her at first sight. However, she disappears suddenly and he only sees her again after nine years, when she is already married. To overcome the pain of losing his love, Dino finds a guru with supernatural power to make him meet Mandy in his dream.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: God of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers"; clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Flying Dragon Leaping Tiger
programme.desc: Lu the horse thief is betrayed by his best mate Qiao and is separated from his son. Lus wife blames him for it and takes Qiaos daughter away as revenge. For 20 years, Lu searches for his wife until one day, his missing son meets Qiaos daughter and they fall in love. Will their hatred pass on to the next generation?

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Come Back Home
programme.desc: In a chilly winter, De and his family goes on a self-drive tour to Changbai Mountain. The holiday turns tragic when Des eight-year-old son goes missing. He seeks help from the local police but is unable to find his son. Though the golden hour has passed, De and the rescue team insist on continuing the search. Can they finally rescue the boy?

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: A Writer's Odyssey
programme.desc: Based on a novel of the same name, this is the story about a father who must kill a novelist in order to find his missing daughter. Through a strange twist of fate, the fantasy world of the novel begins to impact life in the real world.

programme.title: Trivisa
programme.desc: In the beginning of 1997, Hong Kong's three notorious thieves who have never met one another before appear in the same restaurant. This leads to a rumour that they are joining forces to pull off something big before the Handover, though this is not something that any of them is aware of.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Somewhere Winter
programme.desc: The film follows the love story of a university student, An Ran and a Taiwanese man, Qi Xiao. They met and fell in love at a concert by Chyi Chin, a Taiwanese singer, in Beijing in 1991. However, courage alone may not be enough for the lovers to stay together, and goodbyes may truly mean the end. Will An Ran and Qi Xiao meet again in 2019?

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Home Sweet Home
programme.desc: A school bus accident kills almost everyone on board. The bus driver got injured and partially lost his memory while rescuing one of the boys. To thank the driver, the boys dad, Wang, brings him to live with the family in their basement. However, the driver soon discovers strange behaviours from the Wangs which seem to be related to the accident.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: 12 Golden Ducks
programme.desc: This is a comeback story about the misadventures of a group of gigolos, led by Future, trying to make their mark in Hong Kong. As with any profession, they have their share of setbacks, but their ability to find laughter within the tears reflects the drive, passion and the indomitable spirit of the Hong Kong people.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: Blind War
programme.desc: Former SWAT captain Dong Gu suffers traumatic visual loss during a failed mission for which he is forced to take responsibility. He manages to get over and adapt to the situation with his daughters company, until his nemesis appears and puts his daughter in danger. Despite being blind, Dong Gu must fight to save his daughter.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his familys massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: Vengeance is a Golden Blade
programme.desc: Convoy Master Lis wife has an affair with his rival Long, who plans to steal Lis Golden Blade and kill him as well as his young daughter. Li and his daughter manage to escape and the latter grows up to be a skilled swordswoman who vows to avenge her mothers death a lie told by Li. The truth is revealed when she sees her mother alive by chance.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma breaks when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: A Place to Call Home
programme.desc: Li Ching, star of Sweet is Revenge, plays one of three daughters, whose life is turned upside down when she discovers she is adopted. But things get even worse when she goes in search of her real mother. Finally, after what is almost a double tragedy, she realizes what so many knew all along: There's no place like home.

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: The Eight Diagram Pole Fighter
programme.desc: The Yang Generals were ambushed by the enemies and only two of the sons survived. The fifth son of Yangs escapes to Shaolin temple and learns the pole-fighting techniques from the monks, eventually creating his own Eight Diagram Pole Fight and teaming up with the Shaolin monks to avenge his family.

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couples brothel.

programme.title: Duel Of Fist
programme.desc: Fan Ke discovers at his fathers deathbed that he has a half-brother, Wenlie, in Thailand. He goes to find Wenlie, who became a boxer to support his sick mother. Following their encounter, the two got involved in the underworld of boxing match gambling.

programme.title: Fangs of the Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: Yu Lou is betrayed by his wife and eventually killed by her lover, Fung, who is the boss of a martial arts school. Yu Lous brother, Xiao Lou, knows about his tragic death and is determined to take revenge for him.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Starring the stunning, teenage heartthrob Pat Ting Hung, The Butterfly Chalice marks the important directing debut of the kung-fu film genre's most principle figure Chang Cheh, as he burst the martial arts and swordplay movie doors wide open, announcing the beginning of the end for the Cantonese musicals.

programme.title: Danger has Two Faces
programme.desc: Many years ago, Inspector Kam killed an innocent man and decided to resign from the police force. He became a professional killer who disguises as a pet store owner. When his best friend, Bobby begins investigating recent murder cases committed by Kam, he discovers that the mastermind behind these cases is actually his superintendent.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: The 14 Amazons
programme.desc: The Yang family had served their country in Song Dynasty for generations. When General Yang is ambushed and killed during the war in Jin Shan, the grand matriarch led the entire family to take revenge and defend the country.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: The Shadow Whip
programme.desc: Three hundred thousand worth of silver is robbed by a thief using a whip as the weapon. As it is a signature weapon used by a martial arts master Shadow Whip, he is suspected and hunted. No one sees him after that. Fifteen years later, a young girl Yang shows up using the same weapon. Who is this girl and what has happened to Shadow Whip?

programme.title: Sweet And Wild
programme.desc: Fang is a spunky young village girl who is not afraid to fight back against hooligans. She gets into trouble with the biggest hoodlum Tong when she foils his plans with a maid, causing Tong to plot a revenge. Luckily a man whom she is attracted to, Hai, comes in time to her rescue. Can they fight back?

programme.title: The Crimson Charm
programme.desc: In attempting to rescue some innocent people, swordsman Chiang Tzu-chao (Fang Mien) slays the son of Tsao Kang (Wang Hsia), leader of the ruthless Crimson Charm gang.The enraged father promises vengeance on the day of Chiang's 60th birthday...

programme.title: The Tiger and the Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: The Winged Tiger
programme.desc: If the two big villains Winged Tiger and Underworld King join forces, the martial arts world will be plunged into chaos. This evil union is set to occur with the marriage of the Underworld Kings sister and the Winged Tiger. Can this dangerous duo be stopped before one says "I do"?

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: Descendant of the Sun
programme.desc: Shi Sheng is adopted by an old carpenter and grows up to possess extraordinary superpowers. One day, he unexpectedly discovers his identity as the son of the solar deity and learns that his power will be lost during solar eclipse. When an evil spirit appears and wreaks havoc, Shi Sheng must beat him in an ultimate duel to save the world.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword masters daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace. She dies on the run and returns as a spirit to take revenge by killing the evil master, and soon vanishes after returning the sword to the emperor.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: Demon of the Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng Ling is ordered to help find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon. Only Chiao Yin knows the whereabouts of the weapon. Hsiao and her classmate Old Naughty set out on an arduous journey to find Chiao. After overcoming many obstacles, they catch Chin Mo's man trying to snatch the bow and manage to stop him in time....

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: All Men are Brothers
programme.desc: This is a sequel to Chang Chehs epic The Water Margin, and follows the patriotic story of seven warriors in the band of 108 outlaws at Mount Liang. The magnificent seven battle against the despotic government officials to save their country.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Sword Stained with Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yongs novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers?
programme.desc: Jenny Hu, Shaw Brothers' gorgeous Chinese-German star, was given her first comedy role in the wild and wacky Guess Who Killed My Twelve Lovers? Described as "a comedy of belly laughs and chilling murders", it is a unique entry in the Hong Kong theater of the absurd.

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.desc: Camouflage and Colouration - Hiding in plain sight helps many insect, fish, and amphibian species survive. Learn the ins and outs of an array of animal invisibility techniques, such as warning and disruptive colouration, mimicry, and active camouflage.

programme.title: Mysteries of the Mekong 1 Ep10

programme.title: Arabian Inferno 1 Ep5

This episode tells the stories of the majestic raptors and magnificent waders, from the largest migrants to the smaller residents, and how they fly, hunt and survive in this region of extremes - both in the wild desert and close to the urban jungle.

programme.desc: Blood and Dust - Discover the clever way elephants dig wells, and see the relief that comes with a sudden river-filling downpour. Mourn cheetah Kuletas loss after lions kill one of her cubs, and get a front-row seat when wild dog Phoenix faces off with a hyena mob.

programme.title: Wild Dogs: Running with the Pack 1 Ep3

programme.title: Colombia's Wild Coast 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Snake Prison Island - Gorgona was once home to Colombias Alcatraz. Modelled on Nazi concentration camps, prisoners dreamt of escape. See the islands stunning wildlife through the eyes of a convict on the run, the monkeys, snakes and sloths whove now reclaimed the land.

programme.title: Untamed Valley 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Hippo Lagoon - Secluded and sheltered, away from the hustle and bustle of Zambias Luangwa River, Kasikizi lagoon is home to a small community of diverse wildlife. At the height of the wet season, its full to the brim with water a peaceful spot, ideal for two old male hippos who wallow in its watery depths. The lagoon is their sanctuary, a world away from the more violent life theyve left behind at the main river, where they had to face aggressive beachmasters, willing to fight to protect their territory...

programme.title: Untamed Valley 1 Ep2
programme.desc: The Big Bend - The Big Bend is over two miles long one of the biggest meanders along the Luangwa River in Zambia. Its a busy spot - home to a pod of hippos who luxuriate in its deep pools, an important crossing point for elephants and place to drink for huge herds of buffalo.

programme.title: Untamed Valley 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Ebony Plain - Bustling with wildlife, a grassland lies at the heart of Zambias Luangwa Valley known to locals as "The Ebony Plain". Its a busy little neighborhood - home to a family of warthogs, a troop of baboons and a solitary female leopard named Olimba. Watch as life and death unfold on a daily basis in this corner of the Zambian wilds.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep6
programme.desc: November-December - Full Circle - Witness some of the most incredible natural events in November, from the millions of Monarch butterflies that converge in Mexicos forests to the deep fog that shrouds the city of Dubai, signalling the start of winter.

programme.title: Secrets of the Enchanted Forests 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Tropical - Circle the equator for a look at the diverse species that dwell in tropical forests. Meet a lone sloth growing a mini-forest, lemurs that share and share alike, and elephants that tend to their woodland gardens. Then explore the regions dark side.

programme.title: Secrets of the Enchanted Forests 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Seasonal - Watch the seasons wax and wane and learn how trees and animals help one another survive. Witness spring fireflies dancing after dark, discover summer fungi that cool off overheated trees, and prep for autumn migrations as the leaves begin to fall.

programme.title: Secrets of the Enchanted Forests 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Water Worlds - Wade into wetlands, where trees and water meet to nurture new life. Dive into an underwater forest that protects young fur seals, visit a mangrove sanctuary where a curious band of aquatic misfits hides out, and meet some real-life swamp monsters.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep1
programme.desc: Why Elephant Has A Trunk - You see there was a time when Elephant had no nose. He couldn't swat away the flies, or scrub his belly he couldn't even blow his nose. Then one day snappy Crocodile snapped! Crocodile pulled and he pulled and he pulled until Ker-doing!!! Crocodile let go and Elephant's nose was all long and wiggly! And that's why Elephant has a trunk. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep2
programme.desc: Why Snake Has No Legs - You see there was a time when Snake did have legs hundreds and hundreds of them. But poor old Snake had no eyes, not a single eye on his head. Then on the day of the great Tinga Tinga Festival of Colours Snake quite literally bumped into Millipede who was stuck in a hole. They decided to swap eyes and legs just for one day. So that Snake could see all the wonderful colours and Millipede could run all over Tinga Tinga. But when Snake came back to return Millipede's eyes, Millepede couldn't be found anywhere! So to this day, Snake has no legs. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep3
programme.desc: Why Hippo Has No Hair - You see there was a time when Hippo did have hair lots of hair! She was always harumphingly hot. Then one hot night while Hippo was sleeping a spark from the fire caught the end of her hairy tail! Hippo was on fire! She ran through the bush until SPLOSH! Hippo jumped in the waterhole. And from that day on Hippo stayed in the cool waters without a single hair on her hide. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep4
programme.desc: Why Tortoise Has A Broken Shell - You see there was a time when Tortoise's shell was all shiny and smooth. One day Tortoise discovered the birds were having a Feast in the Heavens and he tricked the Birds into making him a pair of wings. Greedy Tortoise raced the birds beyond the clouds and scoffed the whole feastt! When the Birds found out Tortoise had to jump off a cloud until BOOF!!! He landed on his shiny shell. All the animals pieced Tortoise's shell back together but from that day on Tortoise's shell was all bumpy and broken and he never moved speedily again. Tales from Africa.

programme.desc: Postman Pat And The Cornish Caper - Ted Glenn's Cornish cousin Ned is sending him a steam engine as an alternative means to power his workshop. Pat and Jess set off to Cornwall to collect this very large special delivery in the SDS Plane whilst Ted sets about giving away all of his old inventions to the people of Greendale in order to clear out enough space for the engine. After a trip over a very bumpy field and flight in the plane, Pat finally delivers the engine to a now very sad Ted. Maybe the engine will cheer him up but when Pat takes the side off the crate, just a heap of engine parts spill out. The engine was shaken apart on the journey. As the party gets under way in Greendale, the giant pumpkin floats out to sea and Pat and Jess board the SDS Orca and head out into Pencaster Bay. programme.title: Andrew Olle Media Lecture - Leigh Sales Ep2
programme.desc: Sr. 1 - One of Australia's most respected journalists, Leigh Sales, delivers the Andrew Olle Media Lecture, covering the themes of news avoidance, loss of trust in the media, and why, like many people, she is being affected by both.

programme.title: Wildest Australia - Rainforests Ep2
programme.desc: Sr. 1 - Some of the world's most ancient and ecologically diverse rainforests are in Australia, from the oldest tropical rainforest on earth, North Queensland's Daintree, to the stunning central highlands of Tasmania.

programme.title: Strong Women Ep1
programme.desc: Sr. 1 - At the Arnold Australian Strongman Championships, Kerryn and Alira are competing neck and neck for the title of Australia's Strongest Woman under 65kg.

programme.title: That Pacific Sports Show - Pacific Games Special Ep45
programme.desc: Sr. 3 - The Pacific Games have commenced in the Solomon Islands and Sam Wykes, Tinirau Arona and former PNG Olympian Anna-Liza Mopio-Jane visit Honiara to meet local volunteers and athletes.

programme.title: The Pacific - Summer Special Ep17
programme.desc: Sr. 2023 - A look back at some of our favourite stories from the region. In PNG Betel nut traders risk their lives to make an income, Tahiti's ancient art of Tatau, and we hear from renowned Solomon Islands musician Charles Maimarosia.

programme.title: Australian Story - Stepping Up - Elly-May Barnes Ep31
programme.desc: Sr. 2023 - Singer Elly-May Barnes on stepping out of her famous father Jimmy's musical shadow, on the long road to the spotlight and how she channels her physical challenges into a powerful cabaret act.

programme.title: Grand Designs Australia - Dooralong Ep15
programme.desc: Sr. 10 - Electrician Mick takes on the challenge of a lifetime when he and artist wife Belynda decide to build their dream Modernist home in the bucolic Dooralong Valley, on the New South Wales, Central Coast.

programme.title: Aussie Bull Catchers Ep9
programme.desc: Sr. 1 - Kurt Hammar's convoy men, machines and equipment arrives at Cox River. Faced with an oversupplied cattle market, Lach must make a life changing decision. The Cooks have just 24 hours left of catching before their season ends.

programme.title: AFLW - Preliminary Final - Brisbane Lions v Geelong Cats Ep57

programme.title: Alone Australia - Day 2: 10 People Remain Ep2
programme.desc: Sr. 1 - It's the morning after their first night in the wilderness, and the participants are discovering how harsh a Tasmanian winter can be. We see the first "tap outs", as conditions prove too tough for some.

programme.title: Gardening Australia Ep34
programme.desc: Sr. 34 - Jane explores a native garden; Costa meets horticulture educators; Tammy prunes potted plants; Clarence plants out a pond; Millie starts up her spring patch; Sophie tidies insect hotels; plus we meet a potato-growing prodigy.

programme.desc: Sr. 1 - At the Arnold Australian Strongman Championships, Kerryn and Alira are competing neck and neck for the title of Australia's Strongest Woman under 65kg.

programme.title: Anh's Brush With Fame - David Wenham Ep14
